---
title: Treat Day Orzo with Mozzarella, Tomato and Chorizo
description: Orzo is one of the tiniest pasta shapes out there - at first glance you might mistake one for a grain of rice. They make a great addition to soups and stews but today we're letting them absorb some flavourful stock, a little like a risotto. An orzotto if you will. Enriched with chorizo and not one but two types of cheese, it's a real treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5942a4bdc9fd08488d1b78b2-2c584321.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/treat-day-orzo-d3f3433d.pdf
servings: 2
